data.description: Brand new construction that epitomizes modern living! This stunning 3 bed, 2 full bath home is nestled on 1.236-acre lot, offering ample space and tranquility. Step inside to discover an open concept living area adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and entertainment. Kitchen features boasting soft touch wood cabinetry and a sleek kitchen island with butcher block tops. Retreat to the primary bedroom, complete with a spacious walk-in closet. Throughout the home, you'll find vinyl plank waterproof flooring, ensuring both style and durability. Over-sized 2-car garage is equipped with water and drain, while the composite decking on the front porch and concrete patio in the back provide the perfect spots for outdoor enjoyment. The backyard is enveloped by a privacy fence, offering a serene oasis, and a new 10x16 storage building. With engineered wood siding, this home exudes quality and elegance. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity.
